text: Justice Dixon may refer to: *Jane Dixon (judge), Judge of the Supreme Court of Victoria *John Dixon (judge), Judge of the Supreme Court of Victoria *Jonathan Dixon (judge), an Associate Justice of the New Jersey Supreme Court *John Allen Dixon Jr., an Associate Justice of the Louisiana Supreme Court *Luther S. Dixon, a Chief Justice of the Wisconsin Supreme Court *Sir Owen Dixon (1886–1972), sixth Chief Justice of Australia *William C. Dixon, an Associate Justice of the Ohio Supreme Court ==See also== *Brian Dickson (1916–1998), Canadian judge, and Chief Justice of Canada 1984–1990
title: Justice Dixon
